      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>AD攻击取证</h1><p>Author: Wuvoun(253567768@qq.com)</p>
        
          <h1 id="active-directory-攻击取证">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#active-directory-%e6%94%bb%e5%87%bb%e5%8f%96%e8%af%81"></a>
Active Directory 攻击取证
</h1><h2 id="检测-ntdsdit-转储">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%a3%80%e6%b5%8b-ntdsdit-%e8%bd%ac%e5%82%a8"></a>
检测 NTDS.dit 转储
</h2><ul>
<li>
<p>事件 7036</p>
<p>用来记录 <strong>Windows 服务状态的变化,</strong>
如果在日志里发现一些敏感服务被异常启动/停止（如 <em>Remote Registry</em>, <em>WinRM</em>, <em>Telnet</em> 等），就要警惕是否有人在进行横向移动或远程控制。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="使用-ntdsutil-或-windows-内置功能">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8-ntdsutil-%e6%88%96-windows-%e5%86%85%e7%bd%ae%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd"></a>
使用 <strong>ntdsutil</strong> 或 Windows 内置功能
</h3><ul>
<li>转储指令</li>
</ul>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>ntdsutil <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;activate instance ntds&#34;</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;ifm&#34;</span> <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;create full C:\ntdsbackup&#34;</span> quit quit
</span></span></code></pre></div><ul>
<li>取证</li>
</ul>
<p><code>Security.evtx</code> → <strong>4688 (Process Creation)</strong></p>
<p>存在进程  <em><strong>ntdsutil.exe</strong></em>
存在指令  <em><strong>ntdsutil &ldquo;activate instance ntds&rdquo; &ldquo;ifm&rdquo; &hellip;</strong></em></p>
<p>在 IFM 创建数据库副本的过程中，<strong>系统为了避免复制时 NTDS.dit 处于写入状态</strong>，后台会通过 <strong>NTDS 服务调用 Windows 的快照机制</strong> 来生成一个一致性的副本，然后再从快照中提权ntds, 所以会从日志中发现Volume Shadow Copy</p>
<h3 id="使用-esentutl">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8-esentutl"></a>
<strong>使用 esentutl</strong>
</h3><ul>
<li>
<p><strong>转储指令</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>esentutl /y C:<span style="color:#ae81ff">\W</span>indows<span style="color:#ae81ff">\N</span>TDS<span style="color:#ae81ff">\n</span>tds.dit /d C:<span style="color:#ae81ff">\e</span>vidence<span style="color:#ae81ff">\n</span>tds_copy.dit
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>（<code>/y</code> = copy，<code>/d</code> = 转储路径，通常还加 <code>/vss</code> 参数）</p>
        
        <hr><p>Published on 2025-08-26 at <a href='http://localhost:1313/'>Wuvoun</a>, last modified on 2025-08-26</p>]]>
